values.Script:
Dialogue(Would you like to buy some food? $5 for a bite.)
Set(StillShopping, true)
While(StillShopping == true)
   Choice(Show Food Money, Yes, No)
      Case Yes
         If(Money >= 5)
            Incr(Money, -5)
            Incr(FoodSupply, +1)
         If(Money < 5)
            Dialogue(Not enough money!)
            Set(StillShopping, false)
      Case No
         Set(StillShopping, false)

StopFacingPlayer(Me)
Move(Me, Up 5)
Face(Me, Down)
Move(Me, Down 2)
Face(Me, Left)
Move(Me, Left 4)
Face(Me, Right)
Move(Me, Right 3)
FacePlayer(Me)
